title: Episode 156: Move over, you're not eating it right! (Feat. Lloyd)
itunes:title: Episode 156: Move over, you're not eating it right! (Feat. Lloyd)
description:
R&B singer Lloyd joins Lip Service this week and opens up about his past with women, being friends with your ex, and much more. Lloyd shares the news about having a new child and even tells a story in which he spent all his money on Gigi at the strip club. Enjoy! And Stephanie is back too!!
